      "content": "i tried the saline spray but it didnt really do anything and my head is pounding. i'm just so exhausted. i know i should call the doc but i have to work in an hour and they won't pick up for like 3 hours. how bad is the risk really? i only need to take one or two pills to get through the day, surely that wont hurt the baby? it's just a decongestant.",
